    "description": "行銷普遍存在於日常生活及世界的每一角落，而行銷管理是指針對創意、產品與服務所進行的概念化，並就訂價、推廣與配銷等規劃與執行之程序，藉此創造出能滿足個人與組織目標交換活動的一切管理事宜。",
    "prerequisites": "無",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.\t市場導向策略性管理<br>2.\t行銷環境<br>3.\t消費者市場與其購買行為<br>4.\t市場區隔與產品定位<br>5.\t產品策略<br>6.\t價格策略<br>7.\t通路策略<br>8.\t推廣策略<br>",
        "en": "1.\tStrategic management of market-focus<br>2.\tMarketing in a dynamic environment<br>3.\tBuying behavior<br>4.\tMarket segmentation and priduct positioning<br>5.\tProduct and service concepts and strategies<br>6.\tPricing concepts and strategies<br>7.\tMarketing channels and logistics<br>8.\tNtegrated marketing communication<br>"
